nodes.text: Keshani was a female Human who served in the Republic Military during the Galactic War with the reconstituted Sith Empire. During the Quesh war on the planet Quesh, she was stationed at the Republic Operational Headquarters, where she ran the small cantina on the base.
Keshani appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Cantina Vendor for Republic players on Quesh.
